data.description: This home is looking for a new owner.  We have many exciting features that any new owner would love.  Lets start with 2, 2 car garages, one is heated, plus both garages have new roofs 2022. Speaking of new roofs, the house also has a new roof in 2022. Inside we have several updates too, New furnace and AC in 2022, Water heater in 2021. The back yard has an above pool, fenced in yard (new in 2021), plus the yard is a double lot so you have extra yard to play, garden or just let the dogs run.  Other new feature are New Patio Sliding door, 2023, New interior doors, 2023 New Storm door in front  2023.  This is a rare find indeed! The estate is selling this home as is, But the estate is providing a TMI home warranty.
